item.name: Get list of available delivery methods

request.description:
CURRENTLY NOT WORKING 

This method will return all the available last mile couriers and their delivery methods for the requested destination.

Request URL: https://sandbox.eswdb2b.com/api/courier_v1/order/get_delivery_methods/{destinations_id}

Data: destinations_id  destination for which the delivery methods should be returned

item.name: Get list of last mile couriers parcel lockers (PUDO)

request.description:
This method will return all the available parcel locker locations for the requested last mile courier (if available) in the requested destination.

Request URL: https://sandbox.eswdb2b.com/api/courier_v1/order/get_click_collect/{destinations_id}/{pickup_modules_id}

Data:

destinations_id  destination, for which the parcel lockers list should be returned

pickup_modules_id  pickup module key, for which the parcel lockers list should be returned
